title: |md
  # Pool Memory Overhead Calculation
  `overhead_bytes = (chunk_count × sizeof(Chunk)) + (map_size × sizeof(uint64_t))`
  *Reference: Technical Specification M2-11*
| {near: top-center}

direction: right

classes: {
  storage: {
    style: {
      fill: "#E3F2FD"
      stroke: "#1565C0"
      stroke-width: 2
      font: mono
    }
  }
  metadata: {
    style: {
      fill: "#FFF3E0"
      stroke: "#E65100"
      stroke-width: 2
